<a href="dynaminc-balancing-calculator.htm"><img src="images/dynamic-balancing-calculator/static-couple-separation-program-screen.gif" width="110" height="82" alt="dynamic balancing calculator" title="" align="left" />
<b><i>New</i> Dynamic Balancing Calculator.</b></a>  Load this multi-plane dynamic balancing calculator software program to your laptop and easily perform complex dynamic balancing tasks.   This $980 program provides features previously available only with high-end balancing instrumentation that cost over $10,000.
<p>
<b>Do you need your balancing machines calibrated?</b>  Using certification procedures traceable to NIST, we are an economical, independent source for <a href="balancing_machine_calibration.htm"><STRONG>balancing machine calibration and certification.</STRONG></a>
